caller_intent: Evelyn Frost contacted Alliance Insurance to ask about her home insurance renewal and sought assistance with policy-related questions.
resolution_steps: Agent acknowledged the call and asked for the policy number.
Agent mentioned transferring the caller to an agent who could address her questions.
summary: Evelyn Frost called to inquire about home insurance renewal but the agent only confirmed the need for a policy number and mentioned transferring her to another agent. The call ended before any substantive assistance was provided.
